description: The space probe has been studying Jupiter since 2016 and just flew within about 200 miles of the surface of the ice-covered ocean moon.

media:description: A detail of an image captured by NASA's Juno spacecraft during a flyby on Thursday shows the complex, ice-covered surface of Jupiter's moon Europa.
